Australian pelicans are crammed in wing to wing.

21
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:03,450
Some animals appear to be begging to be let
out.

22
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:10,150
"Well, we're close to the animals on a daily
basis -

23
