31
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:19,830
: "Most of all because of the holding facility
they've got is very poor. The humidity is

32
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:26,630
very high and they are very dark inside and
it's easily transmit diseases one

33
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:33,630
to the others and the second thing is, the
exhibit is very old, mostly left over by Dutch

34
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:37,890
maybe 50 years or 70 years ago".

35
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:50,140
Tony Sumampau is one of Indonesia's most respected animal experts, and he's particularly concerned
about some vitally important residents - Surabaya

36
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:57,960
Zoo's Sumatran tigers.: "They have no room
for exercise, for these three tigers in Surabaya Zoo.

37
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:03,560
They have no sunlight when they are growing,

38
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:09,250
so until now they don't have any facility
for them to exercise, to climb the tree, to

39
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:15,590
