like that - that makes their muscle becoming

40
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:22,600
weaker and weaker every day and the food is
not very good as well".

41
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:30,090
The appalling condition of the zoo's Sumatran
tiger population is perhaps the most difficult

42
00:05:30,090 --> 00:05:37,390
to comprehend. These magnificent creatures
should be the pride of Indonesia, the dominant

43
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:45,800
predator among the country's exotic species.
But populations have been devastated by development

44
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:55,060
and poaching. Here at the zoo though, the
picture is no more positive for this critically

45
00:05:55,060 --> 00:06:02,130
endangered animal. "In regard to diseases
that are inside that zoo,

46
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:07,900
there's tuberculosis, there's hepatitis...
