47
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:16,900
There are thought to be only about three to
four hundred Sumatran Tigers left in the wild.

48
00:06:16,900 --> 00:06:23,000
In here, 15 share their cramped quarters with
others like this Bengal Tiger.

49
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:36,200
Sri Penta has seen the best and worst of this
place in her 20 years here. Now, though, it's

50
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:42,080
