176
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:33,420
Indonesia's Forestry Minister, Zulkifli Hasan,
has come to check the conservation efforts

177
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:41,470
at Taman Safari Park. His ministry makes the
rules and regulations for zoos but even a

178
00:22:41,470 --> 00:22:46,570
powerful national politician has found it
difficult to solve the Surabaya mess.

179
00:22:48,570 --> 00:22:55,570
"To revitalise it, to improve the way to manage
the zoo, renovating the cages would take an

180
00:22:55,570 --> 00:23:02,460
immense amount of funds. And the entrance
tickets alone won't cover it. The local government's

181
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:09,500
allocated budget of four billion rupees isn't
enough either. So we need time".

182
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:19,760
And as if financial and management problems
weren't enough, now nature is throwing in

183
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:26,100
