disease developing in already scant wild tiger

184
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:33,500
populations that attacks the nervous system
and eventually kills the animal.

185
00:23:33,500 --> 00:23:39,250
It's just one reason why so much is depending
on the success of a special breeding program

186
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:46,420
