189
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:10,160
success, the program could help keep the wild
Sumatran tiger population alive.

190
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:11,290
"I would think now the tiger's number is really at around 300...
350, nothing more than that.

191
00:24:18,290 --> 00:24:25,590
If we can't save the habitat of the tigers
we might lose the tiger in another 30-40 years.

192
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:34,460
They will disappear in the wild, except in
the zoo".

193
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:47,550
A great deal rests on the survival of Melani,
the tigress as well. If she can survive the

194
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:53,150
ordeal she suffered at Surabaya Zoo it will
inspire and encourage all those who've worked

